\v 7 And \f + \fr 10:7 \ft Heb. and it shall come to passe that when these signes &c.\f*let it be when these signes are come vnto thee, \f + \fr 10:7 \ft Heb. do for thee as thine hand shall finde.\f*\add that\add* thou doe as occasion serue thee, for God \add is\add* with thee.
